) according to Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":9983,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/11\/25\/signs-hour-slaughter-impostors\/","url_meta":{"origin":39714,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Trials: The Hour preceded by great slaughter","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"November 25, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe Hour will not be established until two groups fight each other. There will be a massive slaughter between them, although their claim is one and the same. The Hour will not be established until close\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17739,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/25\/signs-hour-rise-of-fools\/","url_meta":{"origin":39714,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Signs: The Hour is preceded by rise of the foolish","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 25, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah ibn al-Yaman reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe Hour will not be established until the happiest of